    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies. This example is mated to a desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, offering a pure analog connection to the road. The mechanical symphony is supported by a functional M Variable Differential Lock for optimal corner-exit traction. Significant preventative maintenance has been performed, including a VANOS system refresh and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural rigidity. While the exterior shows minor patina from spirited use, the chassis dynamics remain sharp with refreshed bushings and dampers. The interior features Nappa leather with minimal bolster wear. This is a mechanically sound, high-performance machine ready for the canyons.",
