      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a stunning 2017 Porsche 718 Cayman finished in classic Guards Red. This vehicle has been thoughtfully maintained and serves as a perfect example of a well-cared-for enthusiast car. The exterior paint retains a deep, lustrous shine, showing only minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small, professional touch-up on the passenger door. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean; the black leather sport seats are firm and supportive, with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All interior electronics, including the Porsche Communication Management system and the premium sound system, operate flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health with a full service history documented at authorized intervals. A comprehensive major service was completed recently, including new spark plugs and a brake fluid flush. The mid-mounted turbocharged engine delivers smooth, linear power, and the suspension remains tight and responsive. It currently sits on 19-inch alloy wheels with high-performance tires that offer significant tread depth. This Cayman is a turn-key performance machine ready for the open road.",
